T1  - Pricing Warrants: An Empirical Study of the Black-Scholes Model and Its Alternatives
AU  - LAUTERBACH, BENI
AU  - SCHULTZ, PAUL
Y1  - 1990/09/01
PY  - 1990
DA  - 1990/09/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1990.tb02432.x
