T1  - Turn-of-Month Evaluations of Liquid Profits and Stock Returns: A Common Explanation for the Monthly and January Effects
AU  - OGDEN, JOSEPH P.
Y1  - 1990/09/01
PY  - 1990
DA  - 1990/09/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1990.tb02435.x
