T1  - Time Varying Term Premia and Traditional Hypotheses about the Term Structure
AU  - LONGSTAFF, FRANCIS A.
Y1  - 1990/09/01
PY  - 1990
DA  - 1990/09/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1990.tb02439.x
T2  - The Journal of Finance
