T1  - Changes in the Cost of Intermediation: The Case of Savings and Loans
AU  - COMPTE, RICHARD L. B. LE
AU  - SMITH, STEPHEN D.
Y1  - 1990/09/01
PY  - 1990
DA  - 1990/09/01
